1.  <span data-ttu-id="ed7ca-107">Recibe una matriz de <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instancias y crea una nueva matriz de <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instancias que se pasarán a la `Speak` método en un motor de síntesis subyacente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed7ca-107">Receives an array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances and creates a new array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances to be passed to the `Speak` method on an underlying synthesis engine.</span></span>  
  
